- Well then I suggest

1:02:03.070 --> 1:02:03.979
you follow me.

1:02:03.979 --> 1:02:06.896
(thunder rumbles)

1:02:19.779 --> 1:02:21.255
- I don't remember any of this.

1:02:21.255 --> 1:02:23.210
Are you sure we're going the right way?

1:02:23.210 --> 1:02:25.367
- Yeah, it's right up here.

1:02:25.367 --> 1:02:27.700
- We should just look
downstairs for a bathroom.

1:02:27.700 --> 1:02:29.649
This is like walking in circles.

1:02:29.649 --> 1:02:32.312
(ominous music)

1:02:32.312 --> 1:02:33.990
(floor creaks)

1:02:33.990 --> 1:02:35.157
- Ah...
- What?

1:02:36.250 --> 1:02:37.364
- Is that Lilly?

1:02:37.364 --> 1:02:39.599
(ominous music)

1:02:39.599 --> 1:02:42.182
(floor creaks)

1:02:52.165 --> 1:02:54.915
(intense music)

1:02:57.960 --> 1:03:00.200
Lilly, what the hell are you doing?

1:03:00.200 --> 1:03:01.487
Where's Skylar?

1:03:01.487 --> 1:03:04.154
(ominous music)

1:03:11.710 --> 1:03:14.127
(clattering)

1:03:19.540 --> 1:03:22.540
(lightning strikes)

1:03:28.601 --> 1:03:31.268
(intense music)

1:03:33.518 --> 1:03:34.764
(screams)

1:03:34.764 --> 1:03:37.431
(ominous music)

1:03:49.092 --> 1:03:51.842
(footsteps thud)

1:04:03.463 --> 1:04:05.799
(footsteps thud)

1:04:05.799 --> 1:04:07.083
- Skylar!

1:04:07.083 --> 1:04:07.916
Help me!

1:04:07.916 --> 1:04:10.583
(ominous music)

1:04:11.594 --> 1:04:12.766
Skylar!

1:04:12.766 --> 1:04:13.599
Skylar!

1:04:13.599 --> 1:04:16.266
(ominous music)

1:04:24.900 --> 1:04:27.612
(sobs)

1:04:27.612 --> 1:04:30.966
- Maddie, please don't run away.

1:04:30.966 --> 1:04:33.591
I don't know what's wrong with me.

1:04:33.591 --> 1:04:35.367
Maddie, I don't feel so good.

1:04:35.367 --> 1:04:39.826
(sobs) Can you help me, please?

1:04:39.826 --> 1:04:41.076
Maddie, please!

1:04:42.214 --> 1:04:44.131
(sobs)

1:04:46.480 --> 1:04:50.140
- Lilly, what's gotten into you?

1:04:50.140 --> 1:04:51.973
What were you doing with that ax?

1:04:51.973 --> 1:04:52.927
(sobs)

1:04:52.927 --> 1:04:55.667
Where's Skylar and Piper?

1:05:01.190 --> 1:05:03.290
- Have you ever been in a rainbow, Maddie?

1:05:05.020 --> 1:05:05.963
I have.

1:05:07.210 --> 1:05:11.343
They're black inside
and that's where I am,

1:05:12.860 --> 1:05:14.177
in the blackness.

1:05:17.159 --> 1:05:18.909
In the black rainbow.

1:05:21.216 --> 1:05:23.883
(intense music)

1:05:48.654 --> 1:05:50.904
(whimpers)

1:05:53.497 --> 1:05:54.330
(neck snaps)

1:05:54.330 --> 1:05:57.368
(body thuds)

1:05:57.368 --> 1:06:00.035
(ominous music)

1:06:09.430 --> 1:06:12.263
(creepy chanting)

1:06:28.020 --> 1:06:31.020
(heavy metal music)

1:08:17.909 --> 1:08:20.992
(distorted chanting)
